query: SELECT brand, COUNT(*) as total, SUM(CASE WHEN description IS NOT NULL AND LENGTH(description) > 50 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as withDesc, SUM(CASE WHEN specifications IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as withSpecs FROM products WHERE brand IN ('YMC', 'ACE', 'Merck', 'Develosil', 'Thermo Fisher Scientific', 'Restek', 'Agilent', 'Avantor', 'Shimadzu') GROUP BY brand ORDER BY total DESC;
